From: Ian Rogers <irogers@google.com>
Date: Fri, 14 Nov 2025 14:05:47 -0800
Subject: perf evsel: Skip store_evsel_ids for non-perf-event PMUs
Git-commit: d53b4996584b448c5427ba9ab3ec06ec43190043
Patch-mainline: v6.19-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

The IDs are associated with perf events and not applicable to non-perf
event PMUs. The failure to generate the ids was causing perf stat
record to fail.

